rows.label: qst200224_msg0001
rows.name:
Of course you can become happy.
No matter what kind of, money is money.

rows.label: qst200224_msg0002
rows.name:
If you have money,
you can solve anything!

rows.label: qst200224_msg0003
rows.name: You are[ML:Dash ]

rows.label: qst200224_msg0028
rows.name: It's been a while, Glen.

rows.label: qst200224_msg0029
rows.name:
I see[ML:Dash ]
So you were the one who
deceived this girl?

rows.label: qst200224_msg0004
rows.name:
Yeah, that's right.
But, I didn't deceive her.

rows.label: qst200224_msg0005
rows.name:
I only advised her
to follow her true feelings obediently.

rows.label: qst200224_msg0006
rows.name:
She will be saved
by obtaining a large amount of money!

rows.label: qst200224_msg0007
rows.name: Money is salvation, you say?

rows.label: qst200224_msg0008
rows.name:
That's right, Glen.
You can't save people
with the justice you speak of.

rows.label: qst200224_msg0009
rows.name: Humans are creatures of desire!

rows.label: qst200224_msg0010
rows.name:
Covered in greed, they
calmly disparage others.
This is the true nature of humans!

rows.label: qst200224_msg0011
rows.name:
Living as one's greed dictates,
fulfilling one's desires,
that is the path to saving people!

rows.label: qst200224_msg0012
rows.name:
Don't screw around!
How can something like
that be human salvation!

rows.label: qst200224_msg0013
rows.name:
Even without money,
people can live righteously!

rows.label: qst200224_msg0014
rows.name:
Oops, I don't have time to play with
you. A big event is about to start
in Teos Aure now.

rows.label: qst200224_msg0015
rows.name:
Teos Aure, you say?
You, what did you[ML:Dash ]

rows.label: qst200224_msg0016
rows.name:
I gave Fraudrinco
to the monsters around here.

rows.label: qst200224_msg0030
rows.name:
They got 10 times the energy
and started rampaging quite nicely.

rows.label: qst200224_msg0017
rows.name:
Eh!?
I didn't hear anything about that!

rows.label: qst200224_msg0018
rows.name: Why are you surprised?

rows.label: qst200224_msg0019
rows.name:
It's a chance to advertise
the effects of Fraudrinco, you know?

rows.label: qst200224_msg0020
rows.name:
Outstanding effect even on big monsters!
The numbness-inducing drink Fraudrinco!
Now on sale!! Or something like that.

rows.label: qst200224_msg0021
rows.name:
We can make more and more money.
You wished for that too, didn't you?

rows.label: qst200224_msg0022
rows.name: No way[ML:Dash ]

rows.label: qst200224_msg0023
rows.name:
You bastard[ML:Dash ]
How much of a fiend are you!

rows.label: qst200224_msg0024
rows.name:
Seems like you can't
suppress your anger, Glen.

rows.label: qst200224_msg0025
rows.name:
But, you don't have time
to be idling around in a place
like this, do you?

rows.label: qst200224_msg0026
rows.name:
By now, Teos Aure
is probably in
terrible trouble, you know?

rows.label: qst200224_msg0027
rows.name:
Damn it!
I'll settle things with you later.
Don't you run away!
